    public abstract class AbstractCommand
extends java.lang.Object
implements ICommand
    The AbstractCommand class is an abstract class that implements the ICommand interface. It has two fields: name and description. It has two methods: getName and getDescription. It has one constructor: AbstractCommand(String name, String description). It has one toString method: toString(). It has one hashCode method: hashCode(). It has one equals method: equals(Object obj)
